Triggering Lambda with SNS Event

This repo demonstrates sample program to read SNS event in lamabda.

Follow Below Steps to deploy the sample template.
The template Creates SNS Topic, Lambda function and Topic Subscription to Lamabda.

Step 1: Update parameters.json as per your environment.
Step 2: Create a zip of lamabda code and upload to S3 Bucket. (snslambda.zip in this case) 
Step 3: aws cloudformation create-stack --stack-name snslambda --template-body  file://template.yaml [Dont forget to set up aws creds using aws configure before running this command]
